name: Push The Limit!
description: Based on my Experience in NFT for several weeks, it's like riding a bike to chase a speedy car with full of tezos in it which is hard but it's still possible to reach the goal. We need to "pedalling" harder it refers to creating, concepting, shilling, etc. Even though sometimes we feeling tired but never give up, just like we climb the uphill road with riding a bike after we go through it, we will go through the downhill and enjoy it. Hopefully it'll be worth it in the end, Godspeed!
